"usb_edit_h" : "<p class=\&quot;MsoNormal\&quot;><B><span lang=\&quot;EN-US\&quot; style=\&quot;font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial\&quot;>Pomoč za nastavitve pogona USB</span></B></p><p class=\&quot;MsoNormal\&quot;><span lang=\&quot;EN-US\&quot; style=\&quot;font-family:Arial\&quot;> </span></p><a name=\&quot;status\&quot;></a><p class=\&quot;MsoNormal\&quot;><B><span lang=\&quot;EN-US\&quot; style=\&quot;font-family:Arial\&quot;>Stanje</span></B></p><p class=\&quot;MsoNormal\&quot;><span lang=\&quot;EN-US\&quot; style=\&quot;font-family:Arial\&quot;>Če je omogočeno, bo aktiviran račun FTP in uporabnik bo prek programa FTP lahko dostopal do pogona USB.</span></p><p class=\&quot;MsoNormal\&quot;><span lang=\&quot;EN-US\&quot; style=\&quot;font-family:Arial\&quot;> </span></p><a name=\&quot;namepass\&quot;></a><p class=\&quot;MsoNormal\&quot;><B><span lang=\&quot;EN-US\&quot; style=\&quot;font-family:Arial\&quot;>Prijavno ime in geslo</span></B></p><p class=\&quot;MsoNormal\&quot;><span lang=\&quot;EN-US\&quot; style=\&quot;font-family:Arial\&quot;>Prijavno ime in geslo za FTP, ki se uporabljata za pridobitev dostopa do pogona USB prek FTP-ja</span></p><p class=\&quot;MsoNormal\&quot;><span lang=\&quot;EN-US\&quot; style=\&quot;font-family:Arial\&quot;> </span></p><a name=\&quot;sharefolder\&quot;></a><p class=\&quot;MsoNormal\&quot;><B><span lang=\&quot;EN-US\&quot; style=\&quot;font-family:Arial\&quot;>Mapa v skupni rabi</span></B></p><p class=\&quot;MsoNormal\&quot;><span lang=\&quot;EN-US\&quot; style=\&quot;font-family:Arial\&quot;>Po uspešni prijavi v FTP bo ta mapa postala korenska ali domača mapa seje FTP.</span></p><p class=\&quot;MsoNormal\&quot;><span lang=\&quot;EN-US\&quot; style=\&quot;font-family:Arial\&quot;> </span></p><a name=\&quot;accessright\&quot;></a><p class=\&quot;MsoNormal\&quot;><B><span lang=\&quot;EN-US\&quot; style=\&quot;font-family:Arial\&quot;>Pravice za dostop</span></B></p><p class=\&quot;MsoNormal\&quot;><span lang=\&quot;EN-US\&quot; style=\&quot;font-family:Arial\&quot;>Če je potrditveno polje za branje in pisanje označeno, bo uporabnik FTP-ja lahko bral in pisal (operacija FTP PUT) v pogon USB</span></p><p class=\&quot;MsoNormal\&quot;><span lang=\&quot;EN-US\&quot; style=\&quot;font-family:Arial\&quot;>V nasprotnem primeru bo imel uporabnik FTP-ja dostop samo za branje</span></p><p>?</p>",
